userCreatedSince: The time since the user was created
userJoinedSince: The time since the user joined
userCreatedAt: The time the user was created at
memberCount: The number of members in the server
inviterCreatedSince: The time since the inviter was created
inviterJoinedSince: The time since the inviter joined
inviterCreatedAt: The time the inviter was created at
inviterInvites: The number of invites the inviter has
inviteCode: The invite code that the user used to join the server
inviteUses: The number of uses the invite has
inviteURL: The invite url that the user used to join the server
